<!-- =========================== FAQ =========================== -->
<section id="faq" class="section bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 reveal">
      <div class="h-eyebrow mb-3">Help</div>
      <h2 class="font-display h-section text-ink-900">Frequently asked.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl border border-ink-100 divide-y divide-ink-100">
      <details class="group p-6 sm:p-7">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] tracking-tighter text-ink-900">Is Money2Abroad regulated by RBI?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-ink-500" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 4v10M4 9h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-500">Yes. Money2Abroad operates as an Authorised Dealer Category-II under the Reserve Bank of India (License #AD-II/2024/MUM/0782). All transfers are routed under FEMA's Liberalised Remittance Scheme (LRS) up to USD 250,000 per individual per financial year.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group p-6 sm:p-7">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] tracking-tighter text-ink-900">What documents do I need?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-ink-500" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 4v10M4 9h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-500">PAN and Aadhaar — fetched automatically via DigiLocker. For purposes above ₹10 lakh (e.g. tuition), we auto-generate the A1 / A2 form. No manual paperwork.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group p-6 sm:p-7">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] tracking-tighter text-ink-900">How is your exchange rate "mid-market"?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-ink-500" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 4v10M4 9h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-500">We pull live rates from Reuters, Bloomberg, and Refinitiv every 3 seconds and pass them on with zero markup. Your only cost is a transparent 0.45% service fee. Banks typically add 2–4% as hidden FX margin.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group p-6 sm:p-7">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] tracking-tighter text-ink-900">What about Tax Collected at Source (TCS)?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-ink-500" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 4v10M4 9h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-500">TCS of 20% applies on LRS transfers above ₹7 lakh per year (5% for education funded via loan; nil up to ₹7L for education). We auto-calculate, deposit with the IT department, and generate Form 27D in your dashboard.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="group p-6 sm:p-7">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <span class="font-display text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] tracking-tighter text-ink-900">What if a transfer gets stuck?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-ink-500" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M9 4v10M4 9h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-500">99.94% of transfers settle in under 60 seconds. In rare delays, our 24×7 human support (avg. 38-second response) and the SWIFT gpi tracker show exactly where your funds are. Full settlement guarantee, insured by ICICI Lombard.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

